NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::ProveDeps - Add release test to run 'prove'
    on dependent distributions

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::ProveDeps (from Perl distribution
    Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Test-ProveDeps), released on 2020-01-29.

DESCRIPTION
    EXPERIMENTAL.

    This plugin adds the following files:

      xt/release/prove-deps.t

    This test script uses Test::ProveDeps to check your dependent
    distributions.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Test-ProveDeps>.

SOURCE
